### Design Decisions Reached
- Company: klökwork Inc / klökwork AI
- Product: kre8 by klökwork AI
- GitHub org: klokworkai, mono-repo: klokworkai/kre8
- Full component renaming locked (kre8_think→kre8, kre8_agent→konnekt, etc.)
- Component phasing: Phase 1 Pilot, Phase 2.1, Phase 2.2, Phase 3
